{
  "video_id": "DIr-hHL_yzM",
  "title": "A VW Love Story | Classic of the Year 2015",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 137.0,
      "end_time": 2880.0,
      "text": "- [Voiceover] We're just\nso honored and excited"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2880.0,
      "end_time": 4993.0,
      "text": "to share our love for VWs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 4993.0,
      "end_time": 8045.0,
      "text": "which resulted in a love for each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 8045.0,
      "end_time": 13045.0,
      "text": "(upbeat music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24420.0,
      "end_time": 26994.0,
      "text": "- My name is Dawn Kerr,\nand this is my husband Tom."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26994.0,
      "end_time": 27564.0,
      "text": "- Hello."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27564.0,
      "end_time": 29714.0,
      "text": "- And we're newlyweds."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30175.0,
      "end_time": 32451.0,
      "text": "I have the red VW Bug."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32451.0,
      "end_time": 35336.0,
      "text": "It's a '63 red top sunroof Bug."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35336.0,
      "end_time": 38666.0,
      "text": "I bought it when I was 16 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40937.0,
      "end_time": 42906.0,
      "text": "The car's name is Hugo."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42906.0,
      "end_time": 47906.0,
      "text": "I went through school and\ncollege and my career commuting."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48474.0,
      "end_time": 52964.0,
      "text": "- Thirty years ago she\ncame down the driveway"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52964.0,
      "end_time": 54976.0,
      "text": "with a car with a blown up engine."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54976.0,
      "end_time": 58206.0,
      "text": "That started off as a rebuild."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 58206.0,
      "end_time": 60807.0,
      "text": "Then while the car was here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 60807.0,
      "end_time": 63447.0,
      "text": "she's kind of a motorhead, so she asked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63447.0,
      "end_time": 66008.0,
      "text": "\"Hey, can we make this\nthing go a little faster?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66008.0,
      "end_time": 67653.0,
      "text": "Here's what she wanted."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67653.0,
      "end_time": 70050.0,
      "text": "She wanted the car to go faster,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70050.0,
      "end_time": 72610.0,
      "text": "be more reliable, and\nget better gas mileage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72610.0,
      "end_time": 75575.0,
      "text": "all the offset combinations you can have."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 75575.0,
      "end_time": 76901.0,
      "text": "But anyway, we did it."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 79842.0,
      "end_time": 82971.0,
      "text": "- Now, I've met so many friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 82971.0,
      "end_time": 85977.0,
      "text": "and relationships that\nI've had for decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 85977.0,
      "end_time": 88172.0,
      "text": "all through this little car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 88172.0,
      "end_time": 91591.0,
      "text": "and ultimately my life partner."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 95100.0,
      "end_time": 97640.0,
      "text": "- Betty here - all our\nvehicles have names -"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 97640.0,
      "end_time": 102640.0,
      "text": "is a '59 transporter,\nknown as a single cab."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 103165.0,
      "end_time": 105075.0,
      "text": "Found out through some research"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 105075.0,
      "end_time": 109158.0,
      "text": "that it was owned by a father-son team"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 109158.0,
      "end_time": 111786.0,
      "text": "that did a marine service."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 112430.0,
      "end_time": 114543.0,
      "text": "- When he relocated here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 114543.0,
      "end_time": 117550.0,
      "text": "he drove his single\ncab with his belongings"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 117550.0,
      "end_time": 121857.0,
      "text": "cross country all the way\nfrom Florida to California"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 121857.0,
      "end_time": 126857.0,
      "text": "and looked up the local VW\nclub here to meet new people."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 126936.0,
      "end_time": 130024.0,
      "text": "When I found out, \"You drove\nthat truck across country"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 130024.0,
      "end_time": 132727.0,
      "text": "\"and had your Toyota Corolla shipped?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 132727.0,
      "end_time": 133559.0,
      "text": "Oh my gosh."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 133559.0,
      "end_time": 138559.0,
      "text": "When I met him, that was\nthe first impression."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 138741.0,
      "end_time": 141848.0,
      "text": "Then I had at the time,\nwhich isn't here now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 141848.0,
      "end_time": 145038.0,
      "text": "but I had a bus that I was restoring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 145038.0,
      "end_time": 148147.0,
      "text": "and needed some help."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 148147.0,
      "end_time": 149895.0,
      "text": "- She had a 21-window micro bus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 149895.0,
      "end_time": 152576.0,
      "text": "and we were doing what's\ncalled a \"rustoration.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 152576.0,
      "end_time": 154079.0,
      "text": "She didn't want to do the whole full boat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 154079.0,
      "end_time": 158366.0,
      "text": "and so we were just\ntaking some more critical"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 158366.0,
      "end_time": 160296.0,
      "text": "parts of the vehicle that needed repairs."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 160296.0,
      "end_time": 162409.0,
      "text": "I invited Dawn over here to help"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 162409.0,
      "end_time": 165762.0,
      "text": "strip out the interior of\nthe vehicle to save on labor."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 165762.0,
      "end_time": 168505.0,
      "text": "- My understanding is that\nDawn put it out on Facebook,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 168505.0,
      "end_time": 171389.0,
      "text": "if there was anybody\ninterested in helping her"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 171389.0,
      "end_time": 172750.0,
      "text": "do the repairs."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 172750.0,
      "end_time": 174661.0,
      "text": "- [Robert] Thomas replied and said"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 174661.0,
      "end_time": 176225.0,
      "text": "he'd be willing to help her out."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 176225.0,
      "end_time": 177952.0,
      "text": "- We made all these pilgrimages."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 177952.0,
      "end_time": 180065.0,
      "text": "His shop is an hour and a half away."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 180065.0,
      "end_time": 182076.0,
      "text": "- [Marlo] The first time\nthey came to the shop"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 182076.0,
      "end_time": 183905.0,
      "text": "they drove separately."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 183905.0,
      "end_time": 185347.0,
      "text": "The second time they came to the shop"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 185347.0,
      "end_time": 187359.0,
      "text": "they drove together."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 187359.0,
      "end_time": 190000.0,
      "text": "- [Robert] Think a love\nconnection happened right there."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 190000.0,
      "end_time": 191728.0,
      "text": "That was pretty cool."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 191728.0,
      "end_time": 194022.0,
      "text": "(upbeat music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 194022.0,
      "end_time": 195749.0,
      "text": "Eventually I heard they were like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 195749.0,
      "end_time": 196847.0,
      "text": "\"We're getting married.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 196847.0,
      "end_time": 198126.0,
      "text": "I was like, \"Holy mackerel!"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 198126.0,
      "end_time": 199853.0,
      "text": "\"This is really cool.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 199853.0,
      "end_time": 203775.0,
      "text": "I'm honored that it happened at the shop."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 203775.0,
      "end_time": 207107.0,
      "text": "Then Dawn said, \"Hey, would you might be"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 207107.0,
      "end_time": 209810.0,
      "text": "\"interested in marrying us?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 209810.0,
      "end_time": 212654.0,
      "text": "I was like, \"How am I going to do that?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 212654.0,
      "end_time": 215844.0,
      "text": "- When we got engaged the\nfirst thing I said is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 215844.0,
      "end_time": 218099.0,
      "text": "\"Okay, only if we can go to Reno"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 218099.0,
      "end_time": 220557.0,
      "text": "\"and go to the drive-through in Hugo.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 220557.0,
      "end_time": 222955.0,
      "text": "Because that would be my perfect wedding."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 222955.0,
      "end_time": 223808.0,
      "text": "- Why not?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 223808.0,
      "end_time": 225494.0,
      "text": "- He was actually for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 225494.0,
      "end_time": 228420.0,
      "text": "But his family wanted to be there."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 228420.0,
      "end_time": 231082.0,
      "text": "Then your friends are all like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 231082.0,
      "end_time": 233032.0,
      "text": "\"Oh, but then we won't be there.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 233032.0,
      "end_time": 235267.0,
      "text": "So we decided to have a wedding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 235267.0,
      "end_time": 237034.0,
      "text": "but I wanted it to be simple,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 237034.0,
      "end_time": 238883.0,
      "text": "and I didn't want to do a lot of planning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 238883.0,
      "end_time": 240549.0,
      "text": "and I had a lot of nerves."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 240549.0,
      "end_time": 242561.0,
      "text": "We had friends, wonderful friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 242561.0,
      "end_time": 244368.0,
      "text": "that said they would set\neverything up for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 244368.0,
      "end_time": 247498.0,
      "text": "I said, \"I'm going to the races.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 247498.0,
      "end_time": 249854.0,
      "text": "- [Tom] Dawn is a very safe driver."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 249854.0,
      "end_time": 251642.0,
      "text": "She drives a big rig for a living,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 251642.0,
      "end_time": 253877.0,
      "text": "so she can't have any tickets."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 253877.0,
      "end_time": 254751.0,
      "text": "It's real simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 254751.0,
      "end_time": 256823.0,
      "text": "She drives her car like she should,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 256822.99999999997,
      "end_time": 259362.99999999997,
      "text": "and every once in a while she\ntakes it out to the drags,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 259363.0,
      "end_time": 261455.0,
      "text": "and legally races it."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 261454.99999999997,
      "end_time": 265132.0,
      "text": "That's the best of both worlds."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 265132.0,
      "end_time": 267165.0,
      "text": "- I was a little worried about winning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 267165.0,
      "end_time": 269013.0,
      "text": "because it's bracket racing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 269013.0,
      "end_time": 271187.0,
      "text": "and it's a set of eliminations."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 271187.0,
      "end_time": 275190.0,
      "text": "If I kept winning, I was going\nto be late for my wedding."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 275190.0,
      "end_time": 275982.0,
      "text": "- Right."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 275982.0,
      "end_time": 278318.0,
      "text": "That ... would have been an issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 278318.0,
      "end_time": 279361.0,
      "text": "- Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 280086.0,
      "end_time": 284434.0,
      "text": "I went up against a girl named Gloria"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 284434.0,
      "end_time": 289434.0,
      "text": "in one of the semi-final,\nand Gloria beat me."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 289553.0,
      "end_time": 290650.0,
      "text": "I didn't let her beat me."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 290650.0,
      "end_time": 291889.0,
      "text": "They all thought\n- No."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 291889.0,
      "end_time": 293433.0,
      "text": "- maybe I let her beat me\nso I could make my wedding."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 293433.0,
      "end_time": 294572.0,
      "text": "But I was like -"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 294572.0,
      "end_time": 296848.0,
      "text": "Everybody who knew me said, \"Oh, no."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 296848.0,
      "end_time": 298189.0,
      "text": "\"Dawn would not have."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 298189.0,
      "end_time": 300241.0,
      "text": "\"She would have been\nlate for her wedding.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 300241.0,
      "end_time": 303532.0,
      "text": "- [Robert] The presentation\nbasically was us"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 303532.0,
      "end_time": 307249.0,
      "text": "all getting in the top\nof the bed of Tom's truck"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 307249.0,
      "end_time": 309018.0,
      "text": "and actually standing in the bed."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 309018.0,
      "end_time": 311679.0,
      "text": "That was our platform, our deck,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 311679.0,
      "end_time": 314910.0,
      "text": "to marry them in front of the crowd."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 314910.0,
      "end_time": 317977.0,
      "text": "- [Dawn] The bus and the\nBug were flanking it."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 317977.0,
      "end_time": 321090.0,
      "text": "- [Tom] They were kind of\ngroomsman and bridesmaId,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 321090.0,
      "end_time": 322450.0,
      "text": "I guess you might say."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 322450.0,
      "end_time": 325498.0,
      "text": "- Our dog was the ring bearer."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 325498.0,
      "end_time": 327874.0,
      "text": "- Right. That's right."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 327874.0,
      "end_time": 331004.0,
      "text": "- I came to the wedding, changed clothes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 331004.0,
      "end_time": 334356.0,
      "text": "literally got up on the\nsingle cab and had a ceremony."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 334356.0,
      "end_time": 337241.0,
      "text": "Then, of course, there\nwas a party afterwards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 337241.0,
      "end_time": 340044.0,
      "text": "and everybody finally\nleaves late, late at night."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 340044.0,
      "end_time": 343723.0,
      "text": "That's when it dawned on me that I had"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 343723.0,
      "end_time": 348723.0,
      "text": "the racetrack wristband on\nmy wrist the whole ceremony."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 351098.0,
      "end_time": 353474.0,
      "text": "It's in all of our wedding pictures."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 353474.0,
      "end_time": 356868.0,
      "text": "We realized that that was\nthe something blue, maybe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 356868.0,
      "end_time": 358412.0,
      "text": "and nobody pointed it out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 358412.0,
      "end_time": 360179.0,
      "text": "because they thought I\nhad a reason to have it."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 360179.0,
      "end_time": 361784.0,
      "text": "But I didn't even know I had it on."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 361784.0,
      "end_time": 363735.0,
      "text": "- [Robert] You know, with\nthe passion of both of them"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 363735.0,
      "end_time": 366437.0,
      "text": "liking Volkswagens and just the whole,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 366437.0,
      "end_time": 369281.0,
      "text": "overall spectrum of the whole situation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 369281.0,
      "end_time": 370846.0,
      "text": "and how it all fell into play,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 370846.0,
      "end_time": 373229.0,
      "text": "it was pretty cool how it all went down."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 373385.0,
      "end_time": 375011.0,
      "text": "- [Dawn] We have always,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 375011.0,
      "end_time": 378241.0,
      "text": "and this is what bonded me to Tom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 378241.0,
      "end_time": 381837.0,
      "text": "when I met him and he had brought his VW"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 381837.0,
      "end_time": 385088.0,
      "text": "to California from Florida, and drove it"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 385088.0,
      "end_time": 387546.0,
      "text": "instead of the Toyota Corolla,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 387546.0,
      "end_time": 390736.0,
      "text": "that just stole my heart,\nbecause I've always,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 390736.0,
      "end_time": 393662.0,
      "text": "the biggest joy I get is driving my car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 393662.0,
      "end_time": 395572.0,
      "text": "because when I first got it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 395572.0,
      "end_time": 397116.0,
      "text": "it was my daily driver."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 397116.0,
      "end_time": 401809.0,
      "text": "I never want to be that\nperson, personally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 401809.0,
      "end_time": 405324.0,
      "text": "who polishes it up and tows it to a show"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 405324.0,
      "end_time": 407254.0,
      "text": "and tows it home, and actually never"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 407254.0,
      "end_time": 410423.0,
      "text": "enjoys being behind the wheel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 410423.0,
      "end_time": 413857.0,
      "text": "and using it for the purpose it was built,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 413857.0,
      "end_time": 414974.0,
      "text": "and that's rolling down the road"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 414974.0,
      "end_time": 416640.0,
      "text": "and watching the scenery go by."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 416640.0,
      "end_time": 419952.0,
      "text": "They are an organic experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 419952.0,
      "end_time": 421577.0,
      "text": "compared to the new cars today."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 421577.0,
      "end_time": 423122.0,
      "text": "You're in a bubble."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 423122.0,
      "end_time": 424645.0,
      "text": "You can feel the road."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 424645.0,
      "end_time": 426311.0,
      "text": "You can smell the smells."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 426311.0,
      "end_time": 427266.0,
      "text": "They have no air conditioning."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 427266.0,
      "end_time": 428241.0,
      "text": "The windows are open."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 428241.0,
      "end_time": 431848.0,
      "text": "He shares that."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 432065.0,
      "end_time": 437049.0,
      "text": "(upbeat music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 444763.0,
      "end_time": 449763.0,
      "text": "(light music)"
    }
  ]
}